         <abstract id="aspace_7ccbc8f821fe398005274bf0ce436ded">Correspondence, diaries, and other papers of the Rev. James Merriam Howard, chaplain to the 304th Field Artillery during World War I. The bulk of the papers cover the years 1917-1919 and relate to his service in the war and to his diary.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no97012239"
                      source="naf">
               <part>Howard, James M. (James Merriam), 1886-1971</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
